The '''Mixtwirk''' were a small [[Insectoid/Legends|insectoid]] [[Alien/Legends|alien]] race with sensitive antennae on their heads, which they used for hearing. They communicated in squawks. A Mixtwirtk and a [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] patron of [[Stock Lights]] overheard [[Cryle Cavv]] and his nephew [[Sienn Sconn]] discussing plans to steal a [[Galactic Empire|Imperial]] [[Star Destroyer]], and were ejected from the premises by Cavv.<ref name="AJ15">{{JournalCite|15|Two for One}}</ref>

